Package: hipercontracer
Architecture: any
Depends: libhipercontracer1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: hipercontracer-importer,
            hipercontracer-query,
            hipercontracer-trigger
Description: Command-line programs for HiPerConTracer
 High-Performance Connectivity Tracer (HiPerConTracer) is a
 Ping/Traceroute service. It performs regular Ping and Traceroute runs
 among sites. The results are written to data files, which can be
 imported into an SQL or NoSQL database.
 .
 This package contains the actual HiPerConTracer program.

Package: hipercontracer-trigger
Architecture: any
Depends: hipercontracer (= ${binary:Version}),
         libhipercontracer1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Triggered HiPerConTracer service
 High-Performance Connectivity Tracer (HiPerConTracer) is a
 Ping/Traceroute service. It performs regular Ping and Traceroute runs
 among sites. The results are written to data files, which can be
 imported into an SQL or NoSQL database.
 .
 This tool triggers HiPerConTracer by incoming "Ping" packets.

Package: hipercontracer-importer
Architecture: any
Depends: libuniversalimporter1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: hipercontracer,
            pwgen
Description: HiPerConTracer results data importer
 High-Performance Connectivity Tracer (HiPerConTracer) is a
 Ping/Traceroute service. It performs regular Ping and Traceroute runs
 among sites. The results are written to data files, which can be
 imported into an SQL or NoSQL database.
 .
 This package contains the importer tool to import results from
 HiPerConTracer into an SQL or NoSQL database.

Package: python3-queryhelper
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends: python3-mysql.connector,
         python3-psycopg2,
         python3-pymongo,
         python3-snappy,
         python3-urllib3,
         python3-zstandard,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends}
Description: Query helper library for HiPerConTracer Universal Importer
 High-Performance Connectivity Tracer (HiPerConTracer) is a
 Ping/Traceroute service. It performs regular Ping and Traceroute runs
 among sites. The results are written to data files, which can be
 imported into an SQL or NoSQL database.
 .
 The HiPerConTracer Universal Importer query helper library for Python
 is provided by this package.

Package: hipercontracer-query
Architecture: all
Depends: python3-queryhelper (>= ${source:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends}
Recommends: hipercontracer,
            pwgen
Description: HiPerConTracer database query tool
 High-Performance Connectivity Tracer (HiPerConTracer) is a
 Ping/Traceroute service. It performs regular Ping and Traceroute runs
 among sites. The results are written to data files, which can be
 imported into an SQL or NoSQL database.
 .
 This package contains a simple query tool to obtain results
 from a HiPerConTracer SQL or NoSQL database.
